{"tid":19623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特事特辦？ 法庭辦公時間已過 律政司代表始入稟覆核 終獲准辦理","createTime":"2016-12-03T01:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T12:29:05.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f69e6afd0d529c9477f5522e6a2c829d954a28e9","tid":19623,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"傳咗咁多日，律政司今日終於正式入稟高等法院，要求取消立法會議員劉小麗、梁國雄、羅冠聰同埋姚松炎嘅議員資格，袁國強司長強調呢次係根據法律行事。<br />\n<br />\nEmily相信律政司嘅員工為咗準備呢次入稟，最近都應該要加班，唔知係咪因為時間緊迫，結果負責去高等法院入稟嘅幾個律政司代表，趕到去法庭登記處嘅時候，已經過咗下午5點嘅辦公時間。<br />\n<br />\n法庭職員見到有人想話入稟，就講到明辦公時間已經過咗，「5點我要收工喇」，點都唔畀律政司嘅代表入去登記處。呢個時候，其中一位律政司嘅代表喺閘門外大叫：「我係DOJ（律政司）嘅」，法院職員聽到之後態度軟化，話「如果上司畀你入，咪畀你入囉」，之後佢向上司請示咗一陣，就決定打開閘門，畀律政司嘅代表入去登記處，辦理入稟手續。Emily就諗，唔知咁樣又算唔算係「特事特辦」呢？"},{"pid":"b43351e80ee310eb262eff5a241b7548fb388cfd","tid":19623,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一國一制將至"},{"pid":"0148c1deabf439aa9fd75d026c3126e6be1f684e","tid":19623,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:30:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7f20fdd0441b50c9303560fa55a397766d5aba","tid":19623,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:31:11.000Z","msg":"三權合作"},{"pid":"11f21ee98ea2160731e2c8b57998cb4ab66c789f","tid":19623,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"同黑社會無分別"},{"pid":"39316d68fba773f80008945c0ffd95b95c5f0767","tid":19623,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6370e9c772504edc8158509e87021712df00f670","tid":19623,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"好似黑社會撻朵咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06de9c06350806d9e2c602631038512bd3c474a","tid":19623,"uid":2867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三權合作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n極權 not三權合作 <br />\n<br />\n三權合作係支那用黎修飾極權而作出黎"},{"pid":"97827a42ccc4e30263a3d998fa67e82452e430ff","tid":19623,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>三權合作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n極權 not三權合作 <br />\n<br />\n三權合作係支那用黎修飾極權而作出黎</blockquote><br />\n獨裁統治理論上<br />\n軍警 立法機關 法庭都係執政黨統治工具"},{"pid":"1d3cc2870eb2a888a1764899cfba2b49e1cd7539","tid":19623,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"唔使走後門，直接走前門 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a3cd96e8e3834ad12e0e6be96da2a26d2bd264","tid":19623,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:47:20.000Z","msg":"小弟讀得書少唔知咩叫律政司，係咪浩南哥啲fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d62cd4bb4831e54a1c20236af81cc5fcf94e18","tid":19623,"uid":50329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T04:56:14.000Z","msg":"到時法官面前可唔可以用呢件事打佢不符合程序？"},{"pid":"84ffb8ff36099c8a5716657c08d8a6f21a081990","tid":19623,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T12:29:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}